 h Blender to create your 3D object file for printing on a Prusa MK3S+ 3D p
 rinter.\nBasic computer knowledge and experience are required.\nRegistrati
 on is required for this class and begins March 19th\, 2026 at 12:30pm.\nPl
 ease bring your own USB key if you would like to keep your file.\nNote: Yo
 ur spot will not be guaranteed after 5 minutes of the start of the program
 .\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe personal information on this form i
 s collected by the Toronto Public Library under the Public Libraries Act\,
