  they are super-sized. Join us for a fun-filled day of GIANT board games! 
 Play your favourites or try something new! Brings your friends and family 
 or meet new people at the library. Games available for use in the Children
 's area.\nAvailable GIANT games include: Snakes & Ladders\, Checkers\, Sor
 ry\, Cards\, Uno\, Chess\, Tic-Tac-Toe\, Chess\, Connect 4\, Feltro\, Gian
 t Tumbling Tower\, Dominos\, Jenga\, Monopoly
LOCATION:Mimico Centennial\, Children's Area
