BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Hands-On Dinosaur Fossils & Ancient Life
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260317T180000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260317T193000Z
UID:69335f4c8b29ea2800c2c0c1@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an opportunity to handle\, examine up close and di
 scuss nine real and replica fossils in this fascinating hands-on workshop.
  Participants will be entertained and educated\, not just about the fossil
 s themselves\, but the paleontological aspects that underpin them. Concept
 s include: evolution\, fossilization\, 'The Tree of Life' (phylogeny) and 
 - of course - dinosaurs!\nNo registration necessary\, however space is lim
 ited!
LOCATION:Palmerston\, Program Room (downstairs)
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69335f4c8b29ea2800c2c0c1
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
