 \, students will get to try different types of writing and see what fits t
 heir style. By the end\, they’ll walk away with a better sense of how wr
 iting can be fun\, expressive\, and even something you can build a career 
 around.\nDrop In. No Registration Required.
LOCATION:Amesbury Park
