UID:69b43d5667801235ed71c8ae@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Come to Thorncliffe branch and enjoy a family movie during Mar
 ch Break.  Flow (2024) is an award winning and highly acclaimed wordless
  animated film.\nA courageous cat's home is devastated by a great flood. 
 As the cat teams up with a capybara\, a lemur\, a bird\, and a dog to navi
 gate a boat in search of dry land\, the crew must rely on trust\, courage\
 , and their wits to survive the perils of a newly aquatic planet.\nFor chi
 ldren of all ages and their parents and caregivers. Rated PG\, 1 hour and 
 24 minutes.
