 ls themselves\, but the palaeontological aspects that underpin them. Conce
 pts include: evolution\, fossilization\, ‘The Tree of Life’ (phylogeny
 ) and — of course — dinosaurs!\nFor children ages 6-12.\nSpace is limi
 ted. Please register online.
LOCATION:Barbara Frum\, 3rd Floor\, Room B
