BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:FRESH Movie Saturdays
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T150000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T170000Z
UID:696b983ac967cb41208264f0@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:This program helps people stay active\, make friends\, learn n
 ew skills\, and have fun. Meet new folks\, build connections\, and tell us
  about programs and services you would like to see in the neighbourhood!\n
 Come join us every Saturday for screenings of your favourite movies. In ad
 dition to this\, enjoy cuddles with a therapy dog! Therapy dog Goose visi
 ts Fort York Branch on alternate Saturdays from 11:00AM-12:00PM.\nWe'll b
 e showing the following films:\nJanuary 17-Escape to Witch Mountain (2009
 )\nJanuary 24-Finding Neverland\nJanuary 31-Christopher Robin\nFebruary 7-
 Rubt Bridges\nFebruary 14-Akeelah and the Bee\nFebruary 21-The Princess an
 d the Frog\nFebruary 28-Soul\nMarch 7-Batteries Not Included\nMarch 14-Fre
 aky Friday (2003)\nMarch 21-October Sky\nMarch 28-Agent Cody Banks\nDrop
 -ins are welcome.\nThis program is in collaboration with\nGerstein Crisis 
 Centre's F.R.E.S.H. initiative\n.
LOCATION:Fort York\, Urban Living Room
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/696b983ac967cb41208264f0
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
