UID:698b5b24b0595799c09c0048@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Become a forensic scientist and investigate this whodunit by e
 xamining clues left at the scene!  Learn how to interpret evidence by exp
 loring fabric samples and running a chemical analysis on a mystery solutio
