 se chromatography to analyze the ink used in a mysterious note.  Will you
  identify the culprit?\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe personal infor
 mation on this form is collected by the Toronto Public Library under the P
 ublic Libraries Act\, sections 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and 20(d). The information 
