UID:698789f1d34a4e759284f9fb@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:This March Break join us for an opportunity to handle\, examin
 e up close and discuss nine real and replica fossils in this fascinating h
 ands-on workshop. Participants will be entertained and educated\, not just
  about the fossils themselves\, but the palaeontological aspects that unde
 rpin them. Concepts include: evolution\, fossilization\, ‘The Tree of Li
 fe’ (phylogeny) and — of course — dinosaurs!\nAges 6-12.\nInformatio
