UID:698f73898d5e2d09335efd78@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:This interactive workshop is all about helping you level up yo
 ur pitching skills!\nLearn to turn your ideas into powerful stories\, grab
  people’s attention\, and explain what you do in a clear and exciting wa
 y.\nCreate a strong “elevator pitch” — a short\, memorable intro you
  can use anytime\, anywhere — and make a lasting impression on any audie
 nce.\nDrop-in. Limited spots.\nThis is part of the Youth for Entrepreneurs
 hip program led by the YMCA of Greater Toronto. Through hands-on sessions\
 , you’ll gain the digital tools\, financial knowledge\, and creative str
 ategies needed to build a business idea from the ground up.
