UID:69a5cce581b67dfe32a9e306@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Explore one of the possibilities of 3D printings in your daily
  life!\nIn this in-person program\, you will learn how to DIY a keychain b
 y combining traditional macramé braiding skills with new technology 3D de
 sign and printing.\nRegistration will start from 2 weeks before at 9am. In
 tended for ages 13+. Children under 12 years old must accompany with an ad
