DESCRIPTION:Join us for small group visits with therapy dogs. Children wil
 l have an opportunity to read\, listen to stories and engage in therapeuti
 c human-animal interaction. This free program is presented in partnership 
 with One Health Partners.\nChildren who live with a disability\, are neuro
 divergent\, or have experienced medical or other types of trauma are espec
 ially welcome. Suitable for school-aged children ages 6 and up. Siblings a
 ges 6 and up are welcome.\nThere are two 30-minute sessions available: 4-4
 :30 or 4:30-5:00. Please register for one session. Please click on the app
 ropriate program listing to register for that time. There will be limited 
 drop-in spots available on a first come\, first served basis.\nInformation
