BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Nature in your Neighbourhood
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T170000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T183000Z
UID:69a20521491b809c6f1cfe78@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:How well do you know your wildlife? Learn about the unique tra
 its of our local wildlife through a variety of interactive activities. Par
 ticipants will have an opportunity to create their own birdfeeder to take
  home (supplies may be limited).\nThis is an all ages nature program (ages
