 al information sessions. Learn more about the law and discuss your legal r
 ights. Each session will explore a different topic.\nThis workshop will go
  over the requirements to apply for Ontario Works (OW) and Ontario Disabil
 ity Support Program (ODSP)\, how to apply\, and how to challenge decisions
  about social assistance benefits. Spousal support and income deductions w
 hile on social assistance will also be covered.\nRegistration is encourage
 d.\nDrop-ins are welcome until capacity is reached.\nInformation Collectio
