DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260316T220000Z
UID:69811aa6d2bbe265eb2bbe5f@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:TV host and celebrity chef Sang Kim will teach the basics of m
 aking Korean-style kimbap\, exactly like you see them on your favourite K-
 dramas. Participants will roll and cut kimbap using ingredients prepared b
 y the Chef and eat their own creations. A brief history of kimbap\, its di
 fferences from the Japanese sushi roll\, and eating etiquette will also be
