DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260317T190000Z
UID:699cef088b29ea2800d20905@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us with Mad SCIENCE Toronto to explore the science of lig
 ht & colour! Children discover how white light is made and separated into 
 a rainbow of colours.\nFor kids ages 6-12\nSpace is limited.\nTickets will
  be available 30 minutes before the program.
LOCATION:Scarborough Civic Centre\, Program Room
