UID:6999c0541e64afd01e5cfb2c@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Mr. Eric's Musical Adventures is a music lesson packaged in s
 illy fun and nonsense! Through highly engaging and catchy original songs 
 and interactive audience participation\, Mr. Eric teaches rhythm\, rhymin
 g\, song writing\, singing\, movement\, and pitch\, with a big boost of vo
 cabulary to boot! While he’s spent years as a professional orchestra co
 nductor\, Mr. Eric has found a special kind of joy in sharing music and s
 tories with young audiences!\nLIMIT OF 35 CHILDREN. Tickets will be handed
  out 30 minutes prior to the start of the program.\n(Part of Bridlewood's 
 "March Break Fun!" Program Series.)
