  using Rubik’s Cubes to create vibrant pixel art portraits. Participants
  learn basic cube-solving techniques while developing spatial awareness\, 
 logic\, and artistic skills in a fun\, hands-on environment. The program f
 osters teamwork\, patience\, and confidence through engaging\, accessible 
 activities.\nThis program is for ages 6-12 years old.\nRegistration is req
 uired.
