 rmance from Toronto Symphony Orchestra’s Jim Wallenberg. While we welcom
 e children of all abilities\, this program is designed to be especially we
 lcoming to neurodiverse children\, including those on the autism spectrum 
 and those with sensory processing sensitivities.\nRegistration is required
 . Suitable for school-aged children ages 4 and up.
LOCATION:S. Walter Stewart\, Auditorium
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/698243f0834cbb3dea2b5043
