 st like real archaeologists uncover ancient treasures.\nLearn basic excava
 tion techniques\, practice patience and precision\, and discover 12 differ
 ent sparkling stones as you dig your way to treasure. Every participant wi
 ll uncover their own collection of gems to take home!\nPerfect for curious
  minds who love science\, history\, and hands-on adventure.\nDrop-in only\
 , no registration necessary.\nProgram held at the Youth Hub.\nThis program
